{"tid":2131449,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】逃美前港大病毒學家：病毒出自軍方實驗室 籲推翻中共政權","createTime":"2020-07-30T01:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T01:47:09.000Z","uid":226955,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a19e3bf0b8cf8316a28ef82be170c5bd1ba1236a","tid":2131449,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T01:18:01.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200729/FJ3AZML7HGKT3QPWTSJAISH7CM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200729%2FFJ3AZML7HGKT3QPWTSJAISH7CM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhIhk9ljSbOzVJb7ECUhiv3w%3D&h=65c1d19c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200729%2FFJ3AZML7HGKT3QPWTSJAISH7CM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=7e06f816\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200729/FJ3AZML7HGKT3QPWTSJAISH7CM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n曾於香港大學公共衞生學院工作的內地病毒學家閻麗夢，因為擔心遭中共滅口，今年4月逃亡至美國。她於周二（28日）接受YouTube頻道「路德社」專訪時直指，造成全球浩劫的武漢肺炎病毒，就是出自中國軍方實驗室。<br />\n<br />\n閻麗夢表示，她之所以敢於站出來揭露中國隱匿疫情，是因為她看見無辜的武漢醫生和病患都曝露在此高度傳染性的病毒下，身為醫生和科學家，她實在無法無動於衷。閻麗夢更直接點出疫情的爆發源頭是中國軍方，她說：「那時候我已經明確地分析出，病毒是來自中共的軍方實驗室。武漢海鮮市場是一個用來打幌子的地方。」 <br />\n<br />\n閻麗夢說，當她向上級報告卻不獲重視後，她知道不可能再向中共高層反映，「我知道一旦我發聲，隨時我都會被消失，就像香港所有勇敢的抗爭者一樣，隨時可能被消失，連名字都不存在」。她同時強調，自己有責任在「被消失」前將這些訊息曝光。<br />\n<br />\n她還指，自己在中共體系下長大求學，很清楚「中國政府會作出甚麼樣的事情」，只是她無法猜測「（中共的）底線有多低」。閻麗夢表示，她會繼續說出有關中共和疫情的相關真相，希望能加速外界對中共的了解，協助中國人民一起推翻政權。<br />\n <br />\n出生於山東的閻麗夢日前也曾接受美國霍士新聞（Fox News）專訪，指今年1月，武漢肺炎疫情未在香港爆發前，她就曾告知上司、港大公共衞生學院教授潘烈文有關病毒情況及她進行的研究，港大客座教授裴偉士（Malik Peiris，WHO顧問）也知道這情況，但兩人均無視其研究。<br />\n <br />\n閻麗夢說，由於她知道「中國當局為了隱瞞疫情，會如何對待吹哨者」，因此在4月28日搭機離開香港，逃亡美國。<br />\n<br />\nYouTube／台灣《蘋果新聞網》"},{"pid":"08f607be2ee6b7d1a18f3817fc84bcb3ba93da58","tid":2131449,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T01:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a127beb3e30b0f89c5544aa268a3cf35f9f0e1f","tid":2131449,"uid":251621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T01:22:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bd9e0e6a53a0c784dd528416ef85bde04b734097","tid":2131449,"uid":171866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T01:28:15.000Z","msg":"風起了，時代巨輪在轉動"},{"pid":"a9aeaac23e68af47616cc1b631f325d26b9d324a","tid":2131449,"uid":243380,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T01:30:09.000Z","msg":"佢又唔係P4負責一齊整果啲<br />\n點知佢係咪鳩噏"},{"pid":"ac7976768377cb36caff72eb32895bb91aa84476","tid":2131449,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a9aeaac23e68af47616cc1b631f325d26b9d324a","tid":2131449,"uid":243380,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T01:30:09.000Z","msg":"佢又唔係P4負責一齊整果啲<br />\n點知佢係咪鳩噏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T01:32:56.000Z","msg":"美國情報人員唔識fact check咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9bf147c0b366ae6b3d2e867df1c5ba3ffbd98d","tid":2131449,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac7976768377cb36caff72eb32895bb91aa84476","tid":2131449,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a9aeaac23e68af47616cc1b631f325d26b9d324a","tid":2131449,"uid":243380,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T01:30:09.000Z","msg":"佢又唔係P4負責一齊整果啲<br />\n點知佢係咪鳩噏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T01:32:56.000Z","msg":"美國情報人員唔識fact check咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T01:35:25.00